玉米面包给我
See that cornbread.

26
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,410
因为我「实务」经验丰富
Maybe it's 'cause I'm on this seafood diet.

27
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:06,790
看到食物就吃
I see food, I eat it.

28
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,620
好冷哦
That's so bad.

29
