你以前听到都会笑
You always laughed at that one.

30
00:06:11,370 --> 00:06:12,830
那是我12岁的时候
Yeah, when I was 12.

31
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:19,160
一定是芬奇先生
I'm sure it's Mr. Finch.

32
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,790
今天就欠他三个月了
We owe him three months today.

33
