Andy, Andy. Hey, hey, hey.

44
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:01,040
过来
Hey, Andy. Come on. Come on.

45
00:07:02,910 --> 00:07:04,910
我做了什么 -那是诈骗
- What did I do? - It's a scam.

46
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,660
球绝不会在你选的杯子底下
The ball is never under the cup that you pick.

47
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,660
那是诈术
It's a trick.

48
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:10,200
