我想叫它雨迪
I wanna call it Raindy.

53
00:07:21,330 --> 00:07:22,910
你懂吗
Do you get it?

54
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:27,040
雨迪 -我喜欢 很棒
- Raindy. - No, I like it. Yeah, it's good.

55
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:31,200
你去那边等
Okay, so you just wait over there.

56
00:07:31,370 --> 00:07:32,580
我可能要一下子
Okay, I might be a minute.

57
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:34,040
（殖民事务处）

58
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,700
别惹麻烦 好吗
Stay out of trouble, all right?

59
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:38,660
全体员工都将获得照顾
All employees will be seen.

60
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,000
祝你好运
Good luck.

61
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:42,370
请依序排队
Line up in an orderly fashion.

62
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:43,830
下一位
Next.

63
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,790
请问全名和职业
Full name and occupation, please.

64
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:49,200
玛丽雨恩卡拉定 务农
Marie Raines Carradine, ma'am. Farming.

65
00:07:49,370 --> 00:07:50,580
我来申请旅行文件
It's about my travel papers.

66
00:07:51,330 --> 00:07:52,330
（达到额度：可转移）

67
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:54,250
我达到额度 应该能离开了
I met my quota, and I should be free to go now.

68
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:55,700
对吧
Right?

69
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,080
去哪
Go where?

70
00:07:57,250 --> 00:07:58,410
伊瓦加星
Yvaga.

71
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:02,040
它是独立系统 但已完全地球化
It's an independent system, but it's fully terraformed.

72
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:05,120
那里看得见太阳
You can actually see the sun out there.

73
00:08:05,290 --> 00:08:06,660
你的父母呢
Where are your parents?

74
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:10,790
三个周期前去世了
They died three cycles ago.

75
00:08:11,250 --> 00:08:13,000
因为采矿罹患肺病
Lung disease, from the mines.

76
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,450
现在只剩我和我弟
It's just me and my brother now.

77
00:08:16,620 --> 00:08:19,160
他们贩卖希望 使我们甘愿为奴…
They sell us hope to keep us slaves.

78
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:25,540
他们贩卖希望
They sell us hope to keep us slaves. Wake up now.

79
00:08:36,830 --> 00:08:39,700
抱歉 你还没有资格解约
I'm sorry, but you're not eligible for contract release yet.

80
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:42,370
因为缺工 你要被转到矿区
Due to a shortage of workers, you're being transferred to the mines.

81
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:43,830
等等 什么
Wait, what?

82
00:08:44,450 --> 00:08:46,500
不对 我达到要求时数了
No, no, no, I reached the required hours.

83
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:47,910
你们必须让我走
You have to let me go.

84
00:08:48,040 --> 00:08:48,830
（殖民工作合约）

85
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:50,910
可惜额度提高到两万四千小时
Unfortunately, quotas have been raised to 24,000 hours…

86
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,870
你再过五到六年才能解约
so you'll be released from contract in another five to six years.

87
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:56,000
谢谢 别忘了公司非常感谢…
Thank you, and remember the company is really grateful…

88
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,370
你的持续贡献
for your ongoing service.

89
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:59,830
小雨 -喂
- Rain! - Hey!

90
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,080
住手
Hey, stop!

91
00:09:01,250 --> 00:09:03,290
放开他 混蛋
Get off him! You bastards!

92
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:06,790
我在这里
I got you, I got you.

93
00:09:07,250 --> 00:09:08,200
糟糕 你流血了
Shit, you're bleeding.

94
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,040
好
Okay.

95
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:15,620
你没事
You're okay.

96
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:17,120
我把你重置
I'm resetting you.

97
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:18,450
我帮你
I got you.

98
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,250
没事
It's okay.

99
00:09:22,410 --> 00:09:23,830
我不该让你落单的
I shouldn't have left you alone.

100
00:09:29,370 --> 00:09:32,870
他们贩卖希望 使我们甘愿为奴…
They sell us hope to keep us slaves.

101
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,080
醒醒吧  你们就是奴隶
Wake up now. They own you.

102
00:09:38,370 --> 00:09:39,200
嗨 小雨
Hi, Rain.

103
00:09:39,370 --> 00:09:41,040
抱歉我整天一直打给你
Look, I'm sorry. I know I've been calling you all day…

104
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:44,290
因为有事情 应该让你知道
but, look, something's come up, and I think you should know about it.

105
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:47,000
到拖车这边来 带上安迪
So, come by the trailers and bring Andy.

106
00:10:17,290 --> 00:10:18,290
嗨
Hey.

107
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:20,410
拜…
Oh, for…

108
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:22,000
游戏结束
Game over, man.

109
00:10:22,540 --> 00:10:25,080
小雨 好久不见
Sup, Rain? Long time no see.

110
00:10:25,450 --> 00:10:27,040
我就说她会出现
I told you she'd show up.

111
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:29,000
你欠我五块钱
You owe me five bucks.

112
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,330
安迪
Andy!

113
00:10:34,250 --> 00:10:36,290
盲眼矿工怎么会掉进井里
Why'd the blind miner fall down the well?

114
00:10:36,450 --> 00:10:37,790
为什么
Why?

115
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:40,790
因为他有点瞎
'Cause he couldn't see that well.

116
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,330
拜托别怂恿他
Please don't encourage him.

117
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,000
进去吧 我马上过去
All right, go inside. I'll be there in a second.

118
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,330
小凯 -小雨
- Kay. - Rain.

119
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,540
嗨 -嗨
- Hi. - Hi!

120
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:55,790
嗨
Hi.

121
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:58,500
我好想你
I missed you.

122
00:10:58,660 --> 00:11:00,500
我知道我哥也很想你
And I know my brother missed you, too.

123
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,080
真高兴你来了
I'm really glad you came.

124
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:10,580
我听说了你们爸爸的事
I heard about your dad.

125
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:11,750
真的很遗憾
I'm really sorry.

126
00:11:12,540 --> 00:11:15,790
在每个周期的雹暴和新疾病之间…
Well, between the hailstorms and the new diseases every cycle…

127
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:17,500
对 大家都快死了
Yeah, everybody's dying, right?

128
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,330
该给她看吗
So, should we show her?

129
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:21,200
给我看什么
Show me what?

130
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:25,950
昨晚 我们把货放上铁索特
Okay, so, last night, we're loading up the last Tesotek…

131
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:28,700
离地约200哩 突然间…
we're about 200 miles above the ground, and then all of a sudden…

132
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:31,950
船上收到信号
The hauler picks up this beacon.

133
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,120
纳瓦洛追踪它 结果…
So Navarro tracks it, and it turns out…

134
00:11:34,290 --> 00:11:37,200
有艘巨型威兰船舰在我们头上漂流
there's this big Wey-Yu ship drifting right above our heads.

135
00:11:37,370 --> 00:11:38,250
漂流
Drifting?

136
00:11:38,410 --> 00:11:40,040
退役 废弃了
Decommissioned. Abandoned.

137
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,160
残骸 大概受损或被淘汰了
Some old relic. It's probably damaged or obsolete.

138
00:11:42,330 --> 00:11:43,540
就像那家伙
Like that guy over there.

139
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:44,700
比约恩
Bjorn.

140
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:48,250
好 告诉她吧
Okay, just tell her.

141
00:11:48,410 --> 00:11:50,000
我们为何要坐在这里
Why are we all sitting around here…

142
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:53,500
等待公司永远不会发的旅行许可
waiting for travel permits that the company are never gonna give to us?

143
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:56,080
那艘船有动力带我们去伊瓦加星
'Cause that hauler has enough power in it to get us to Yvaga.

144
00:11:56,250 --> 00:11:59,040
因为到伊瓦加星要九年
Because it takes nine years to get to Yvaga…

145
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:01,290
没有冻眠就到不了
and you can't make that trip without cryo-sleep.

146
00:12:01,450 --> 00:12:04,040
退役船还载着许多可用装备
Decommissioned ships still carry tons of functional equipment.

147
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:07,540
超链接显示那艘船还剩几个冻眠舱
And the hyperlink shows that ship still has a few pods left.

148
00:12:11,370 --> 00:12:14,540
你们想闯入威兰的船
You want to break into a Weyland-Yutani ship 

149
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:17,160
偷走高度管制装备
and steal highly regulated equipment?

150
00:12:17,330 --> 00:12:18,540
捷足先登啊
Before someone else does.

151
00:12:20,450 --> 00:12:21,660
你们疯了
You guys are insane.

152
00:12:21,830 --> 00:12:22,950
当然 -才怪
- Well, of course we are. - No. No, we're not.

153
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,330
这是… -我也这么说
- This is… - That's what I said.

154
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,700
你会帮我们吗
Are you gonna help us?

155
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,910
抱歉 需要我做什么
Sorry, what do you need me for?

156
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,080
安迪
Andy.

157
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:35,160
我们需要用到安迪 -安迪
- We need to use Andy. - Andy?

158
00:12:35,330 --> 00:12:36,160
嗯
Mm-hmm.

159
00:12:36,330 --> 00:12:39,080
他是威兰合成人 能跟母亲沟通
He's a Weyland-Yutani synthetic. He speaks Mother.

160
00:12:39,250 --> 00:12:40,620
他能进入船上的终端机
He can access a terminal on the ship to get us in 

161
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:42,200
让我们轻松进出
and out without a fuss.

162
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:43,620
只有那样才能进去
It's the only way to get in.

163
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:45,870
要是我们被逮到呢
Okay, but what if we get caught?

164
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:48,500
获得旅行许可的机会就没了
It'll ruin our chances of ever getting a travel permit.

165
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:50,200
好 小雨不去
Right, Rain's not comin'.

166
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,620
不然你让我们带安迪去
How about you let us take Andy then?

167
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:55,790
我才不让我弟自己上去
I'm not sending my brother up there alone.

168
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:57,660
他不是你弟吧
He's not your brother though, is he?

169
00:12:57,830 --> 00:12:59,870
比约恩 给我闭嘴 -没错啊
- Bjorn, shut the fuck up. - It's true, though, isn't it?

170
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,290
他不是你弟 只是威兰的瑕疵品
He's not your brother. It's just Wey-Yu damaged goods…

171
00:13:01,450 --> 00:13:02,910
你爸在垃圾里找到的
that your dad found in the trash.

172
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:05,000
如此而已 认清现实吧
And that's all he is, Rain. So just wake up.

173
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:06,830
我们走
Let's go.

174
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,580
小雨 -怎样 我又没说什么
- Rain? - What? I didn't say anything.

175
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:10,080
小雨 等等
Rain, wait.

176
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:13,000
抱歉 我表弟有时很机车
I'm sorry. Listen, I know my cousin can be a dick sometimes, all right?

177
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,830
可是他说对了一件事
But he is right about something.

178
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:16,540
你得认清现实
You need to wake up.

179
00:13:16,950 --> 00:13:19,040
这家公司什么都不会给我们
Because this company, they're not gonna give us anything.

180
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,200
你也明白我们只能放手一搏
You know that as well as I do. We have to take it.

181
00:13:25,410 --> 00:13:26,450
小雨 我…
Rain, I just…

182
00:13:27,250 --> 00:13:29,000
我不想落得跟我们爸妈一样
I don't want to end up like our parents.

183
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:30,950
你想吗
Do you?

184
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,500
你们的计划有听起来那么容易吗
Is it as easy as you're making it sound, this plan of yours?

185
00:13:40,500 --> 00:13:42,410
你根本不必离开科布伦号
You won't even have to get out of the Corbelan.

186
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,540
这点我能保证
That much I can promise you, okay?

187
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:50,120
好啦 你愿意吗
Come on. What do you say?

188
00:14:14,450 --> 00:14:16,000
比约恩 快 走了
Bjorn, hurry up, let's go.

189
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:23,040
好 我要发动了 启动电池
All right, I'm starting her up. Batteries on.

190
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:26,540
很好
Lovely.

